text: Southwest Florida International Airport (ICAO: KRSW, IATA: RSW) is a county- owned airport that serves the city of Fort Myers, Florida. The following airlines serve Southwest Florida International: *Air Canada *American Airlines *Cape Air *Delta Air Lines *Frontier Airlines *JetBlue Airways *Silver Airways *Southwest Airlines *Spirit Airlines *Sun Country Airlines *Sunwing Airlines *Swift Air *United Airlines *WestJet ==References== Category:Airports in Florida
title: Southwest Florida International Airport
